blessed ladies Forwarded by Charlotte BanksEnron Communications on AM Jynell ES AM To cc bcc Charlotte BanksEnron Communications Subject Friends who Pray together stay together Lets pray Dear Lord I thank You for this day I Thank You for my being able to see and to hear this morning Im blessed because You are a forgiving God and an understanding God You have done so much for me and You keep on blessing me Forgive me this day for I have sinned I ask now for Your forgiveness Keep me safe from all danger and harm Let me start this day with a new attitude and plenty of gratitude Let me make the best of each and every day and give my best in all that is put before me Clear my mind that I can hear from You Broaden my mind that I can accept all things Let me not whine and whimper over things I have no control over Let me continue to see sin through Your eyes and acknowledge it as evil And when I sin let me repent and confess with my mouth my wrongdoing and receive the forgiveness of God and sin no more And when this world closes in on me let me remember Jesus example to slipaway and find a quiet place to pray Its the best response when Im pushed beyond my limits I know that when I cant pray You listen to my heart Continue to use me to do Thy Will Continue to bless me that I may be a blessing to others Keep me strong that I may help the weak and unsaved Keep me uplifted that I may have words of encouragement for others pray for those who are lost and cant find their way I pray for those who are misjudged and misunderstood I pray for those who refuse to share a word from You I pray for those who dont know You intimately I pray for those who will only read this and not speak this aloud in their own lives I pray for those who will delete this without sharing it with others I pray for those who dont believe But I thank you that I believe I believe that God changes people and God changes things I pray for all my sisters and brothers For each and every family member in their households I pray for peace love and joy in their homes that they are out of debt and all their needs are met There are no circumstance or situation greater than God Every battle is in His hands for Him to fight I pray that these words be received into the hearts of every eye that sees them and every mouth that confesses them willingly This is my prayer In Jesus Name Amen

FW A Positive Thoughtblessed this week Forwarded by Charlotte BanksEnron Communications on AM Claudette NRON PM To cc bcc Charlotte BanksEnron Communications Subject FW A Positive Thought A POSITIVE THOUGHT If God had a refrigerator your picture would be on it If He had a wallet Your photo would be in it He sends you flowers every spring and a sunrise every morning Whenever you want to talk Hell listen He can live anywhere in the universe and He chose your heart What about the Christmas gift He sent you in Bethlehem not to mention that Friday at Calvary Face it Hes crazy about you Send this to the people youre crazy about

FW Black Manthought this was cute I wanted to share Forwarded by Charlotte BanksEnron Communications on AM Claudette NRON AM To cc bcc Charlotte BanksEnron Communications Subject FW Black Man A Black Man A Black Man walks into a bank in New York City and asks for the loan officer He says hes going to Europe on business for two weeks and needs to borrow The bank officer says the bank will need some kind of security for the loan so the Black Man hands over the keys to a new Rolls Royce The car is parked on the street in front of the bank he has the title and everything checks out The bank agrees to accept the car as collateral for the loan The banks president and its officers all enjoy a good laugh at the black man for using a Rolls as collateral against a loan An employee of the bank then proceeds to drive the Rolls into the banks underground garage and parks it there Two weeks later the Black Man returns repays the and the interest which comes to The loan officer says Sir we are very happy to have had your business and this transaction has worked out very nicely but we are a little puzzled While you were away we checked you out and found that you are a multimillionaire What puzzles us is why would you bother to borrow The Black Man replies Where else in New York City can I park my car for two weeks for only and expect it to be there when I return A Smart Black Man Get more from the Web FREE MSN Explorer download

FW Fwd FW PERSONALITY TESTYOULL LOVE THIShave fun with this Original Message From Randle Claudette Sent Wednesday October PM To Eugenia McDonald Email Reginald Daniels Email Email Sammy Lee OBrient Email Email Preston Linda Gordon Takiyah Lipscomb DeMonica Banks Charlotte Winfrey Joan Lacour Paula Scyrus Labricia Coronado Margaret Subject FW Fwd FW PERSONALITY TESTYOULL LOVE THIS Thought you guys might enjoy this Have fun Subject FW PERSONALITY TESTYOULL LOVE THIS Something to do on you spare time haha Dont peek at the answers Learn something about yourself This ones a little different for everyone Okay first get a piece of paper and label it from Now remember you need to give serious thought to these questions What is your favorite of these three a cat b bird c dog What is your favorite of these three a pink b white c black Name a person of the same sex Name a person of the opposite sex Which do you like better the mountains or the beach Which do you like watching more the sunrise or the sunset What is your favorite number from What plant do you prefer more a a red rose b a fern c a dead one What is your favorite season a Spring b Winter c Summer Make two wishes NOW for the RESULTS a cat you love yourself themost b bird you like hearing yourself talk c dog you put others before yourself a pink youre outgoing b white youre classical c black youre living on the edge That person is your lucky star Youll become very very close with them a mountains fastpaced wedding b beach slowpaced wedding a sunrise youre a morning person and you get more done b sunset youre romantic and you fall in and out of crushes slowly The number you picked is how many it will take before you find your true love a red rose your life will be beautiful but sometimes thorny b fern your life will be predictable and safe c a dead one youre one sick person a spring youre hopelessly romantic b winter youre a hugging kind of person c summer youre a bare all kind If you send this to a one person your first wish will come true b five people both of your wishes will come true c ten or more people your wishes will come true in two days YOU HAVE MINUTES Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at intlasp
